|colspan="3" font-size:90%|Modifié par : Williams et al. 2001.<ref name = "Williams">Williams, J. et al. 2001. ''Biodiversity, Australia State of the Environment Report 2001'' (Theme Report), CSIRO Publishing on behalf of the Department of the Environment and Heritage, Canberra. {{ISBN|0-643-06749-3}} [http://www.deh.gov.au/soe/2001/biodiversity/pubs/biodiversity.pdf .pdf]</ref><small>
